title.rendered: AFN LOOPLESS FRONT BAR – NISSAN NAVARA NP300

content.rendered:
AFN LOOPLESS FRONT BAR TO SUIT NISSAN NAVARA NP300!

AFN loopless front bar to suit Nissan Navara NP300 available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The pictured front bar features;

  • Full Bumper Replacement
  • Rated Recovery Points
  • Dual Antenna Tabs
  • Winch Compatible
  • Hi-Lift Jack Points
  • Fog/Indicator Light Assemblies
  • Matte Black Powder Coated

PLEASE NOTE: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order. 

To view the range of products available for your Nissan Navara, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
